title: The Huge Power and Potential Danger of AI-Generated Code
description: Programming can be faster when algorithms help out, but there is evidence AI coding assistants also make bugs more common.

title: Reddit Is Already on the Rebound
description: Despite mass protests by users and moderators, Reddit's unique communities look likely to survive the rebellion over the company's new business strategy.

title: Instagram Is Removing Sex-Positive Accounts Without Warning
description: The platform has suddenly suspended dozens of high-profile accounts, cutting people off from the communities that keep them safe.

title: Wagner Mutiny Puts Russia’s Military Bloggers on a Razor’s Edge
description: Telegram “war correspondents” have promoted the Kremlin's invasion of Ukraine, but many have also supported mercenaries who launched a failed coup.
